<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Nährwertangaben – Röckles Wengert</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --green-bg: #2f6b3a;
      --green-dark: #234f2a;
      --accent: #f5f5f5;
      --font-main: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: var(--font-main);
      background: var(--green-bg);
      color: #ffffff;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 32px 16px;
    }

    .page {
      max-width: 1100px;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .header-title {
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .header-brand {
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .header-divider {
      width: 80px;
      height: 1px;
      background: #ffffff;
      margin: 18px auto 0;
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

    .grape-icon {
      margin: 18px auto 0;
      width: 80px;
      height: 60px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .grape-icon::before,
    .grape-icon::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1px solid #ffffff;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .grape-icon::before {
      width: 14px;
      height: 14px;
      left: 18px;
      top: 26px;
      box-shadow:
        16px 0 0 0 #0000,
        8px -12px 0 0 #0000,
        24px -12px 0 0 #0000;
    }

    .grape-icon::after {
      width: 14px;
      height: 14px;
      left: 26px;
      top: 38px;
      box-shadow:
        16px 0 0 0 #0000,
        -8px 0 0 0 #0000;
    }

    .grape-stem {
      width: 26px;
      height: 26px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1px solid #ffffff;
      border-bottom-color: transparent;
      border-left-color: transparent;
      position: absolute;
      left: 18px;
      top: 4px;
      transform: rotate(-25deg);
    }

    .content {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .content {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    .wine-card {
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 20px 22px 22px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
      box-shadow:
        0 18px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    }

    .wine-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .wine-name {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .wine-year {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      opacity: 0.85;
    }

    .wine-meta {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      opacity: 0.85;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .wine-meta span + span::before {
      content: "•";
      margin: 0 6px;
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

    .nutri-title {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      opacity: 0.9;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .nutri-per {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      opacity: 0.8;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .nutri-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    .nutri-table tr + tr td {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    }

    .nutri-table td {
      padding: 6px 0;
    }

    .nutri-label {
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .nutri-value {
      text-align: right;
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    }

    .nutri-footnote {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      opacity: 0.75;
      margin-top: 10px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page">
    <header class="header">
      <div class="header-title">Nährwertangaben</div>
      <div class="header-brand">Röckles Wengert</div>
      <div class="header-divider"></div>
      <div class="grape-icon">
        <div class="grape-stem"></div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="content">
      <!-- Wein 1 -->
      <article class="wine-card">
        <div class="wine-header">
          <h2 class="wine-name">Riesling trocken</h2>
          <span class="wine-year">2023</span>
        </div>
        <div class="wine-meta">
          <span>11,5 % vol</span>
          <span>enthält Sulfite</span>
          <span>750 ml</span>
        </div>

        <div class="nutri-title">Durchschnittliche Nährwerte</div>
        <div class="nutri-per">pro 100 ml</div>

        <table class="nutri-table" aria-label="Nährwerttabelle Riesling">
          <tr>
            <td class="nutri-label">Brennwert</td>
            <td class="nutri-value">290 kJ / 69 kcal</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="nutri-label">Fett</td>
            <td class="nutri-value">&lt; 0,5 g</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="nutri-label">davon gesättigte Fettsäuren</td>
            <td class="nutri-value">&lt; 0,1 g</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="nutri-label">Kohlenhydrate</td>
            <td class="nutri-value">2,0 g</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="nutri-label">davon Zucker</td>
            <td class="nutri-value">2,0 g</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="nutri-label">Eiweiß</td>
            <td class="nutri-value">&lt; 0,5 g</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="nutri-label">Salz</td>
            <td class="nutri-value">&lt; 0,01 g</td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <p class="nutri-footnote">
          Angaben gerundet. Alkohol trägt maßgeblich zum Brennwert bei.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Wein 2 -->
      <article class="wine-card">
        <div class="wine-header">
          <h2 class="wine-name">Spätburgunder Rosé</h2>
          <span class="wine-year">2023</span>
        </div>
        <div class="wine-meta">
          <span>12,0 % vol</span>
          <span>enthält Sulfite</span>
          <span>750 ml</span>
        </div>

        <div class="nutri-title">Durchschnittliche Nährwerte</div>
        <div class="nutri-per">pro 100 ml</div>

        <table class="nutri-table" aria-label="Nährwerttabelle Spätburgunder Rosé">
          <tr>
            <td class="nutri-label">Brennwert</td>
            <td class="nutri-value">305 kJ / 73 kcal</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="nutri-label">Fett</td>
            <td class="nutri-value">&lt; 0,5 g</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="nutri-label">davon gesättigte Fettsäuren</td>
            <td class="nutri-value">&lt; 0,1 g</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="nutri-label">Kohlenhydrate</td>
            <td class="nutri-value">2,4 g</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="nutri-label">davon Zucker</td>
            <td class="nutri-value">2,4 g</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="nutri-label">Eiweiß</td>
            <td class="nutri-value">&lt; 0,5 g</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="nutri-label">Salz</td>
            <td class="nutri-value">&lt; 0,01 g</td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <p class="nutri-footnote">
          Werte können je Jahrgang leicht variieren.
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
